cha_list.desc:
<#SevenDaysAWeek Challenge with TikTok>

Join Jung Kook’s #SevenDaysAWeek challenge to win a chance to be in the ‘Seven (feat. Latto)’ compilation video. 

* How to Participate: 
1. Create a TikTok video of your own that shows your moment with ‘Seven (feat. Latto)’ 
(You can use dance, role play, duet, acting, etc.)
2. Upload your video using #SevenDaysAWeek and set your video to public and allow download.
3. Complete your submission for your video to be used by the special compilation video by uploading your TikTok video link below.

Submission Link : bit.ly/3DuZx2d

*Submission period: July 14th 01:00 AM ~ July 24th 11:00 AM (Eastern Time)
*This event may be changed or canceled due to unforeseen circumstances of BIGHIT MUSIC and TikTok.
